text: Kamini Kaushal (born Uma Kashyap; 24 February 1927) is an Indian actress. She acted in Neecha Nagar (1946) and Biraj Bahu (1955), both of which won her acting awards. Recently, she acted in Chennai Express (2013) and the romantic drama Kabir Singh (2019). ==References== Category:1927 births Category:Living people Category:Indian movie actors Category:Indian stage actors Category:Indian television actors
